messages.messageBody:
on 7/31/03 12:52 PM, Tracy at vtl.bobsin@... wrote:

> I need help! My computer crashed and I can't remember my yahoo password. I'm
> going on vacation and don't want my inbox to fill up while I'm away. I'm not
> able to make changes to my account. I want to go no mail or unsub from this
> group while i'm gone. What do I do??

Address an email to:

AlwaysLearning-unsubscribe@yahoogroups.com

then

AlwaysLearning-subscribe@yahoogroups.com

when you get back

or

AlwaysLearning-nomail@yahoogroups.com

then

AlwaysLearning-normal@yahoogroups.com or
AlwaysLearning-digest@yahoogroups.com

Joyce
